{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The CMS was born to make content sites "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"possible"}]},{"type":"text","value":". Now, it’s being reimagined to make them "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"incredible"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In the early 2000s, publishing on the web was difficult. The CMS emerged as a single application to store content, build sites, and deliver them to users."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Over time, the feature landscape broadened — key areas like search, analytics, payments, personalization, and e-commerce emerged. In each category, specialized tools improved rapidly, while the quality of monolithic enterprise CMS applications like Adobe Experience Manager and Sitecore has stayed roughly the same."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"modularizing-the-cms"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#modularizing-the-cms","ariaLabel":"modularizing the cms permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Modularizing the CMS"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Today, a website team running an e-commerce site can store product inventory in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.shopify.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Shopify"}]},{"type":"text","value":", product listings in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.salsify.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Salsify"}]},{"type":"text","value":" and reviews in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.bazaarvoice.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bazaarvoice"}]},{"type":"text","value":". A team running a paywalled content site can create stories in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://wordpress.org/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Wordpress"}]},{"type":"text","value":", store video in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.jwplayer.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"JWPlayer"}]},{"type":"text","value":", user data in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://auth0.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Auth0"}]},{"type":"text","value":", and subscription data in "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://recurly.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Recurly"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When website teams want to add search, they can turn to "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.algolia.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Algolia"}]},{"type":"text","value":"; for payments, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://stripe.com"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stripe"}]},{"type":"text","value":"; for analytics, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://segment.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Segment"}]},{"type":"text","value":"; for A/B testing, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.optimizely.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Optimizely"}]},{"type":"text","value":"; for personalization, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.evergage.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Evergage"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Teams are adopting these services because each is tailored to a specific use-case; the generic enterprise CMS alternative is often optimized for none."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"figure","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-link"],"href":"/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/18681/modular-cms-architecture.png","style":"display: block","target":"_blank","rel":["noopener"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"],"style":"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 786px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-background-image"],"style":"padding-bottom: 53.39213025780191%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-image"],"style":"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px #ffffff;","alt":"The modularization of the CMS","title":"","src":"/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/75efb/modular-cms-architecture.png","srcSet":["/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/bea6c/modular-cms-architecture.png 197w","/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/9f6c6/modular-cms-architecture.png 393w","/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/75efb/modular-cms-architecture.png 786w","/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/43bd5/modular-cms-architecture.png 1179w","/static/89fbf8a288ca241618daa69293e1f97a/18681/modular-cms-architecture.png 1474w"],"sizes":["(max-width:","786px)","100vw,","786px"]},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"figcaption","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n   The modularization of the CMS\n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"emergence-of-the-content-mesh"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#emergence-of-the-content-mesh","ariaLabel":"emergence of the content mesh permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Emergence of the Content Mesh"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"This is the first post in a series, Journey to the Content Mesh, intended to explain the emergence of a “content mesh” — the infrastructure layer for a decoupled website. The content mesh stitches together content systems in a modern development environment while optimizing website delivery for performance."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The previous generation of enterprise CMS offered an often-generic content editing experience glued to out-of-date development and deployment environments. The emerging strategy for content management selects best-of-breed solutions, tailored to specific use-cases like e-commerce or blogging; it provides a modern framework for rapid iteration and it generates lightning fast websites out of the box."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"three-areas-of-rapid-innovation"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#three-areas-of-rapid-innovation","ariaLabel":"three areas of rapid innovation permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Three Areas of Rapid Innovation"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Change is being spurred by the confluence of three revolutions in how we create and consume content:"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"ul","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Content management."}]},{"type":"text","value":" Monolithic CMS applications are being replaced by modular, specialized content systems."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Development techniques."}]},{"type":"text","value":" Modern UI frameworks like React are becoming essential to rich user experiences."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"li","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Performance."}]},{"type":"text","value":" As mobile surpasses 50% of internet traffic, high-performance is becoming a must-have, not a nice-to-have."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"figure","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-link"],"href":"/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/51705/three-website-revolutions.png","style":"display: block","target":"_blank","rel":["noopener"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-wrapper"],"style":"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 786px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    "},{"type":"element","tagName":"span","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-background-image"],"style":"padding-bottom: 60.77419354838709%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n      "},{"type":"element","tagName":"img","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-image"],"style":"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px #ffffff;","alt":"Three areas of rapid innovation","title":"","src":"/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/75efb/three-website-revolutions.png","srcSet":["/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/bea6c/three-website-revolutions.png 197w","/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/9f6c6/three-website-revolutions.png 393w","/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/75efb/three-website-revolutions.png 786w","/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/43bd5/three-website-revolutions.png 1179w","/static/0628c2b1ba9cda8dba50deea54df20bf/51705/three-website-revolutions.png 1550w"],"sizes":["(max-width:","786px)","100vw,","786px"]},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n    \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"figcaption","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n    Three areas of rapid innovation\n  "}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"These technological changes have made modern web technology both "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"essential"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for creating fresh, novel, and engaging digital experiences, and "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"more accessible"}]},{"type":"text","value":" for the enterprise."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Each change primarily affects a different stakeholder --- marketing, development/IT, and the end-user, respectively."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The key challenge is that without a content mesh, integrating these systems together is a lot of work. Forrester titled one of their "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://www.tangomodem.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/the-rise-of-the-headless-cms.pdf"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"report sections"}]},{"type":"text","value":": “Warning: Headless Content Management Is For Do-It-Yourself Shops.” But "},{"type":"element","tagName":"em","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"with"}]},{"type":"text","value":" a content mesh, all of these systems can be brought together in a unified, low-cost, low-defect whole."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"integrating-modern-technologies-without-the-diy-work"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#integrating-modern-technologies-without-the-diy-work","ariaLabel":"integrating modern technologies without the diy work permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"Integrating Modern Technologies Without the DIY Work"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"As this series continues, we’ll explore the rise of this “content mesh” — that allows enterprises to adopt these new technologies without needing to DIY themselves."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In Part 2, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/blog/2018-10-10-unbundling-of-the-cms"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Unbundling of the CMS"}]},{"type":"text","value":", we’ll explore the rise of headless CMSs and best-of-breed website content and functionality systems."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In Part 3, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/blog/2018-10-11-rise-of-modern-web-development"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"The Rise of Modern Web Development"}]},{"type":"text","value":", we’ll detail the maturing of the JavaScript ecosystem, the emergence of stable UI libraries like React for creating rich web technologies, and how they help website teams at scale build high-quality sites."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In Part 4, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/blog/2018-10-16-why-mobile-performance-is-crucial"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Why Mobile Performance is Crucial"}]},{"type":"text","value":", we’ll discuss the ROI of site speed, explore two modern, complementary trends for improving web performance and how website teams can get the best of both out of the box."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"In our conclusion, "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"/blog/2018-10-18-creating-compelling-content-experiences"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Creating Compelling Experiences"}]},{"type":"text","value":", we’ll discuss a step-by-step approach for choosing a content architecture, modern development environment, a performance strategy — and most importantly, choosing a “content mesh” that makes all the other choices easy. We’ll also explore how one clear option — Gatsby — emerges as the most feature-complete of any content mesh alternatives."}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"the-modern-website-landscape"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#the-modern-website-landscape","ariaLabel":"the modern website landscape permalink","className":["anchor"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"The Modern Website Landscape"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"figure","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n  \n  "},{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"className":["gatsby-resp-image-link"],"href":"/static/dbb9c824aafc29eea6bb87f1527751f3/f4c82/content-mesh.png","style":"display: block","target":"_blank",